{"tid":2197500,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★40納米手機有無商機？","createTime":"2020-09-10T15:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T18:06:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6541a98ec4b1066e375d655d1fe09f04d86e159e","tid":2197500,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:57:35.000Z","msg":"中芯即將邁向全國產的40納米世紀。雖然，官方講明未能用於手機，但40納米的確曾用在手機製作當中，是10多年前的先進工藝。<br />\n<br />\n40納米基本上是在45到32之間過度時的產物，於2008年開始面世，到2010年32納米出現後，基本上已被淘汰。<br />\n<br />\n同時代有什麼手機呢？翻查資料，它們是：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">--Galaxy S2（首款40納米，到S3已進入32製程）<br />\n<br />\n--iPhone 4 （Apple A5/ 用45＋32雙核）<br />\n<br />\n--HTC Desire HD （45nm，到One X同樣進入32製程）<br />\n<br />\n--Nokia N79（45nm，用ARM11）<br />\n</span><br />\n那麼，中芯生產類近 iPhone 4級數的手機，賣到其他手機市場會否仍有出路？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/40-%E7%B4%8D%E7%B1%B3%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%89%E7%84%A1%E5%95%86%E6%A9%9F-064657309.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F40-%25E7%25B4%258D%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%25A9%259F-064657309.html&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=a987fb13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/40-%E7%B4%8D%E7%B1%B3%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%89%E7%84%A1%E5%95%86%E6%A9%9F-064657309.html</a>"},{"pid":"25c6b0e7a6deab18ce211f7324e147208524a4f4","tid":2197500,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:58:18.000Z","msg":"iPhone 4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nmany lihkg son still strong hold crab<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c